Path: godot/classes/class_editorexportplatformwindows.rst
Summary: Describes the EditorExportPlatformWindows class, which customizes Windows build handling.

The Windows exporter customizes how a Windows build is handled. In the editor's "Export" window, it is created when adding a new "Windows" preset.
